These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, accountant, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, german, polish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, basketball
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, car, trike
1. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the german is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the bartender is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the accountant is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
6. the polish is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | bartender        | accountant     | nurse    |
| Nationality   | polish      | dutch     | german |
| Sport         | soccer | basketball | swimming   |
| Transport     | trike        | car      | helicopter        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, cola
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, writing, photography
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, tram, subway
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person drinking tea##2
3. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage    | fanta    | cola | tea |
| Hobby       | writing   | photography  | baking  |
| Pet         | guinea-pig      | chinchilla     | hamster    |
| Transport   | car | subway    | tram        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, firefighter, musician
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, thai
3 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, dog
1. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the nurse is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the ferret and the musician##2
4. the thai is on the left or right of the nurse##3
5. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Hobby         | reading | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Job           | musician     | firefighter    | nurse |
| Nationality   | australian      | thai     | pakistani |
| Pet           | dog         | turtle      | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: avocado, lime, cauliflower
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, video-games
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, french
1. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating cauliflower is between the french and the person eating avocado##2
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up | juice       | hot-chocolate   |
| Food          | avocado   | cauliflower   | lime     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | video-games  |
| Nationality   | turkish | argentine | french |

