.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: mango, peach, cauliflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, blues, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, taxi
1. the person driving the motorbike is between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person eating peach is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person eating peach and the person eating cauliflower##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the fan of soul##1
8. the person eating peach is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | iced-tea    | water   |
| Food          | cauliflower | mango  | peach |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | rock | soul  |
| Transport     | skateboard | motorbike   | taxi  |

