.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, artichoke, cucumber
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, doctor, architect
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, family
3 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, turtle
1. the person eating radish is the owner of the goat##1
2. the photographer is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
3. the architect is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating radish is the owner of the goat##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
6. the person eating radish is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the turtle and the doctor##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | radish | artichoke    | cucumber  |
| Job           | doctor      | photographer  | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | scientific   | family  |
| Pet           | goat      | hamster | turtle        |

