.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, almond-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, videographer, social-worker
3 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, soccer
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the videographer##1
2. the scientist is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
6. the scientist is the person drinking milk##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate         | almond-milk      | milk   |
| Job        | social-worker | videographer          | scientist |
| Pet        | bird         | rabbit        | turtle       |
| Sport      | tennis       | soccer | weightlifting       |

