There 3 different types of food: zucchini, cabbage, corn
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, chinese, pakistani
1. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
3. the chinese is the chinese##1
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the italian and the chinese##2
7. the fan of rock is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
