.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, collecting, singing
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, lacrosse
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, snowmobile
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's hobby is singing and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | singing   | collecting | camping  |
| Pet         | rabbit      | goldfish      | guinea-pig   |
| Sport       | basketball      | lacrosse       | volleyball |
| Transport   | airplane | snowmobile       | ship     |

