There 3 different types of food: blueberry, cherry, apricot
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, hiking, baking
3 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, snake
1. the person eating apricot is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating cherry##2
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating cherry##1
4. the person eating apricot is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the mouse##2
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | cola    | fanta |
| Food       | cherry          | apricot     | blueberry       |
| Hobby      | baking       | hiking | chess |
| Pet        | cat          | snake       | mouse        |

