3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1

