4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
7. the person eating pomegranate is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
