.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, coffee
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, journalist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, thriller, documentary
3 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, frog
1. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
4. the analyst is on the far left##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
7. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee | lemonade  | 7up |
| Job           | analyst  | journalist  | firefighter      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | thriller | western     |
| Pet           | frog  | fish | hedgehog         |

 